/addCustomers = to create customer and Transaction records
/customers = to retrieve all customers
/transactions = to retrieve all transactions
/customers/{customerId} = get customers based on customerId
/updateCustomer/{customerId}?transactionAmount = update customer points based on the transactionAmount provided.
/updateCustomer/{customerId}/points?startDate&endDate = update customer points based on the date range (3 months old transactions points can be added to existing points).
/delete/{customerId} = delete Customer based on customerId.